bilingual.source: They also sell ice cream, coffee and drinks.
bilingual.target: 他们还卖冰淇淋、咖啡和饮料。

bilingual.source: Amy thinks it's hard to sell her old things.
bilingual.target: 艾米觉得卖掉她的旧东西很难。

bilingual.source: You can sell tickets or work at a food stand.
bilingual.target: 你可以卖票或在食品摊工作。

bilingual.source: But isn't it hard to sell some of your things?
bilingual.target: 但是卖掉你的一些东西不是很难吗？

bilingual.source: She has also set up an online business to sell them.
bilingual.target: 她还建立了一个在线业务来卖包。

bilingual.source: We have decided to each sell five things that we no longer use.
bilingual.target: 我们决定每人卖掉五件不再使用的东西。

bilingual.source: If you buy things you do not need, soon you will have to sell things you need.
bilingual.target: 如果你买不需要的东西，很快你就得卖掉需要的东西。

list.abstract: sell（英[sel]，美[sel]），英语单词，作动词为卖；出售；说服。作名词为出卖；出售；失望。短语搭配有sold out（售罄）。例句为“Day to sell baked sweet potatoes.（今天是卖烤红薯的日子。）”。 sell动词类近义词有promote、find a market等，相关反义词有buy。过去式为sold。过去分词为sold。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I kinda wanted to sell the cookies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很想去卖饼干。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd like to sell all my clothes, please!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想把我所有的衣服都卖掉，拜托啦！

yingyinNormal.en: How are you ever going to sell this place?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你要怎么把房子卖掉？

yingyinNormal.en: I bet we could sell that sign all over Pasadena.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我打赌这种牌子一定能在帕萨迪纳大卖。

yingyinNormal.en: Trust me, this house is gonna sell at Thorpe speed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 相信我，这房子会以索普光速卖出的。

yingyinNormal.en: I know. They probably shouldn't sell those to children.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我懂你。这种产品就不该卖给孩子。

yingyinNormal.en: If we sell them, we will have enough to start a new life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 卖了它们足够我们开始新生活。

yingyinNormal.en: You understand what I'm saying, right? You do sell bonds, don't you, old sport? I'm trying to.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道我在说什么，对吧？你是卖债券的，是吧，老伙计？我正在努力卖。

yingyinNormal.en: Miss Rabbit is ill. You've got to sell the ice-cream today. Oh, I am an expert of ice-cream.
yingyinNormal.zh: 兔小姐生病了，今天需要你来替她卖冰淇淋了。哦，我可是很擅长卖冰淇淋的。

yingyinNormal.en: Miss Rabbit is ill. You've got to sell the ice-cream today. Oh, I am an expert of ice-cream.
yingyinNormal.zh: 兔小姐生病了，今天需要你来替她卖冰淇淋了。哦，我可是很擅长卖冰淇淋的。

yingyinNormal.en: I asked you to take care of it. Why on earth would you sell it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我当时让你妥善保管的，你为什么要卖了它？

yingyinNormal.en: She sells cards and homemade jewels, she said she wanted to sell them. I said, okay. And in one week, I made a $156.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她卖一些卡和自制首饰，她说想卖呢，我答应了，一周里我赚了156美刀。

yingyinNormal.en: Rupert Murdoch should cut me a check for all the papers I sell for him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 默克多得好好谢我帮他卖了那么多报纸。

yingyinNormal.en: And we don't sell drugs, just menus, so the only lie you'll be telling is we print on recycled paper. We don't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不卖药，只卖菜单。所以你唯一要说的谎是我们用再生纸印菜单。其实不是。

yingyinNormal.en: You sell closets and blinds? I could understand shutters and blinds or closets and... We're good, Nancy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们卖橱柜和窗帘吗？一般不是卖百叶窗和窗帘 或者橱柜和……我们公司生意很好，南希。

yingyinNormal.en: What are you doing? I can't sell that now. You suck air through your mouth, you moron.
yingyinNormal.zh: 干什么?现在不能卖，用嘴巴吸气，白痴!

yingyinNormal.en: Come on, don't listen to him. Fast Tony would sell his own mother for a grape.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别听他的，火速东尼为了一颗葡萄，连妈妈都肯卖。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, good luck to Dad. Say, how many more boxes would you have to sell in order to win?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就祝爸爸好运吧，要卖多少盒饼干才能获胜？

yingyinNormal.en: And finish this hellhole so I can sell it. Yeah. I'm sorry about the triplets.
yingyinNormal.zh: 修整好这个鬼地方。我好卖了。好的。对于三胞胎的事我表示遗憾。

yingyinNormal.en: Alicia, don't try to sell me. You are the governor's wife. Your name means something.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾丽西娅，别把我卖了，你是州长夫人，你的名字意味着些什么。

examination_example.sentence: Like other start-up investors, Mr. Arnold's own business often depends on <highlight>selling</highlight> start-ups to larger tech companies.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 像其他初创企业投资者一样，阿诺德自己的业务通常依赖于将初创企业出售给大型科技公司。

examination_example.sentence: The product they're <highlight>selling</highlight> is data, and we, the users, convert our lives to data for the benefit of the digital giants.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们销售的产品是数据，而我们这些用户正在把我们的生活转化成巨头产生利益的数字。

examination_example.sentence: But successive governments have presided over <highlight>selling</highlight> green spaces, squeezing money from local authorities and declining attention on sport in education.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但历届政府都兜售过绿地，从地方政府榨取钱财，并减少对体育教育的关注。

examination_example.sentence: "The way you pre-<highlight>sell</highlight> a movie in a foreign market is based on relevant talent," he says.
examination_example.sentence_trans: “你在国外市场预售电影的方式是基于相关人才，”他说。

examination_example.sentence: I think we're a long way away from having virtual beings that have the ability to pre-<highlight>sell</highlight> content.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我认为，我们距离拥有能够预售内容的虚拟实体还有很长的路要走。

examination_example.sentence: So when advertisers try to <highlight>sell</highlight> me ways to "turn back the clock", I have to suppress a laugh.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因此，当广告商试图向我推销“让时光倒流”的方法，我不得不抑制住笑声。

word_usage.usage:
sell作动词表“出售，售卖”时，为瞬间动词，不可与表示一段时间的状语连用。
他把车卖掉一年了。
误 He sold his car for a year.
正 He sold his car a year ago.
sell for/at，均表示“以…价格出售”。sell for表示“总价”，sell at表示“单价”；sell by表示“以某种单位（如“斤”“两”）或方式（如“零售”“批发”）出售某物”。
畅销，可用sell well表达，不可说sell good，且作“畅销”解时，句子主语只能是物，不能是人。如：我们的产品畅销世界32个国家。Our product sells well in 32 countries in the world.
